rows.label: qev031205_MSG0001
rows.name:
Wroooagh! Lavina will be my mate!
Whoever stole her will pay![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031205_MSG0002
rows.name:
Wrooooagh! I will kill Earth alien who stole Lavina!
Then make her my mate![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031205_MSG0003
rows.name: Lavina married another! What do I do now?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031205_MSG0004
rows.name: ...I know! I will eat bellyful of meat.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031205_MSG0005
rows.name: Eat until sleepy. Then sleep to forget![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031205_MSG0006
rows.name:
Wroooagh! My betrothed canceled engagement!
Is this end for Wazdo and Lavina?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031205_MSG0007
rows.name: NO! She has not wed Earth alien yet![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031205_MSG0008
rows.name:
I will not give up. Not until day I wed Lavina and
feast on beast meat until dawn.[ST:wait ]
